{%- comment -%}
  mega-menu-image-badge.liquid
  ----------------------------
  Renders an image + optional badge text next to a mega-menu item.

  Reads (in priority order):
    link.object.metafields.bv.menu_image  -> Per-link image
    link.object.metafields.bv.menu_badge  -> Per-link badge text
  Fallback:
    /assets/menu-{handle}.jpg             -> Per-collection default
    blank                                 -> No image rendered

  `link` is the menu link object (Shopify exposes
  `linklists.<menu>.links` which contains either a Collection,
  Product, Page or URL object). When `link.object` is a collection or
  product Shopify also gives you `link.object.metafields.<ns>.<key>`.

  Pass `parent_handle` from the surrounding loop so the snippet knows
  which top-level menu group it belongs to (used in fallback image
  filename).

  Usage in `sections/header.liquid`:

    {%- for link in linklists.main-menu.links -%}
      {%- for child in link.links -%}
        {%- render 'mega-menu-image-badge',
                   link: child, parent_handle: link.handle -%}
        <a href="{{ child.url }}">{{ child.title }}</a>
      {%- endfor -%}
    {%- endfor -%}

  All visual styling is in `assets/theme.css` under `.bv-mega-img-badge`
  (see README) — no inline <style>.
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- liquid
  assign menu_image = nil
  assign menu_badge = ''
  assign handle     = link.object.handle | default: link.handle | default: ''

  if link.object.metafields.bv.menu_image
    assign menu_image = link.object.metafields.bv.menu_image
  endif
  if link.object.metafields.bv.menu_badge
    assign menu_badge = link.object.metafields.bv.menu_badge | strip
  endif

  comment
    Fallback to /assets/menu-{parent_handle}-{handle}.jpg first, then
    /assets/menu-{handle}.jpg. The merchant uploads PNG/JPG to Files and
    references them by filename via `image_url`.
  endcomment
-%}

<span class="bv-mega-img-badge">
  {%- if menu_image -%}
    {{- menu_image | image_url: width: 240 | image_tag: alt: link.title, loading: 'lazy', widths: '120,240,360' -}}
  {%- elsif handle != blank -%}
    {%- assign fallback_a = 'menu-' | append: parent_handle | append: '-' | append: handle | append: '.jpg' -%}
    {%- assign fallback_b = 'menu-' | append: handle | append: '.jpg' -%}
    {%- if images[fallback_a] -%}
      <img src="{{ fallback_a | asset_url }}" alt="{{ link.title | escape }}" loading="lazy" width="240" />
    {%- elsif images[fallback_b] -%}
      <img src="{{ fallback_b | asset_url }}" alt="{{ link.title | escape }}" loading="lazy" width="240" />
    {%- endif -%}
  {%- endif -%}

  {%- if menu_badge != blank -%}
    <span class="bv-mega-img-badge__badge">{{ menu_badge | escape }}</span>
  {%- endif -%}
</span>
